The elpAudio music player program (in future, 'program') is a simple audio player 
using FMODex sound system by Firelight Technologies. 
The modification of program's source code is permitted, but for public purposes you should add this text:
"The program was made from elpAudio's source code. Get it free at github.com/elpoeprod/elpAudio".

Distribution the program, program's source code or program, made by user, for commercial purposes is prohibitted,
but you can ask owner of elpAudio, elpoep.